    "title": "Kuja kwa Roho wa Mungu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kuja kwa roho wa mungu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kwenye Agano la Kale, Roho wa Mungu wakati mwingine &quot;alikuja juu&quot; ya watu kuwapa nguvu kwa ajili ya kazi ya Mungu na kutabiri (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:2\">Hesabu 24:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">Waamuzi 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">1 Samweli 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:5\">Ezekieli 11:5</a>). Wakati wa Yesu, watu wengi waliamini kwamba Roho wa unabii alikuwa ameondoka Israeli baada ya manabii wa mwisho wa Agano la Kale. Hata hivyo, manabii walitabiri kwamba wokovu wa Mungu utakapokuja, angemimina Roho wake kwa kila mtu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:15\">Isaiah 32:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:26-Ezek36:27\">Ezekieli 36:26–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:32\">Yoeli 2:28–32</a>).</p><p>Unabii huu unatimia kwanza katika simulizi ya kuzaliwa kwa Yesu katika Injili ya Luka. Roho Mtakatifu aliwahamasisha manabii kushuhudia na kuongoza matukio ya kuzaliwa kwa Yesu.</p><p>Roho alijaza Yohana Mbatizaji hata kabla ya kuzaliwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:15\">Luka 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:41\">41</a>). Baba yake, Zekaria, aliimba wimbo wa sifa kwa Mungu uliojaa Roho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:67\">1:67</a>). Maria, mama wa Yesu, alipata mimba ya Yesu na alitabiri kupitia nguvu za Roho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:35\">1:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:46-Luke1:55\">1:46–55</a>). Roho alimwongoza mzee Simeoni kwenda hekaluni kumwona Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25-Luke2:27\">2:25–27</a>). Baadaye, Roho alimtia mafuta Yesu katika ubatizo wake na kumpa nguvu kutimiza jukumu lake kama Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:21-Luke3:22\">3:21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1\">4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">18</a>).</p><p>Baada ya Yesu kupaa mbinguni, alitimiza unabii wa Agano la Kale kwa kuwatumia wanafunzi wake Roho wake siku ya Pentekoste. Hii iliwawezesha kueneza habari njema (injili) ya wokovu duniani kote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:49\">Luka 24:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">Matendo 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:4\">2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17-Acts2:18\">17–18</a>). Katika kitabu cha Matendo, kanisa lilitekeleza misheni yake kwa mwongozo, nguvu, na mwelekeo wa Roho Mtakatifu. Kuwasili kwa Roho kunaanza enzi mpya ya wokovu wa Mungu. Uwepo na nguvu za Mungu sasa ziko ndani na miongoni mwa watu wake kupitia Roho Mtakatifu.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:2\">Hesabu 24:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">Waamuzi 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">1 Samweli 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:15\">Isaya 32:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:5\">Ezekieli 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:26-Ezek36:27\">36:26–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:32\">Yoeli 2:28–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:15\">Luka 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:35\">35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:41\">41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:67\">67</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:24-Luke2:27\">2:24–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:22\">3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1\">4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:49\">24:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:4\">Matendo 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17-Acts2:18\">17–18</a></p>",
